long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Description:

Website Contact Collector is a powerful extension designed for telemarketing professionals and marketing teams. Its primary function is to streamline the process of collecting website addresses for telemarketing campaigns.

With this extension, you can easily scrape contact addresses from various websites. Simply navigate to the website you want to collect data from, and use the extension to extract contact information such as email addresses, phone numbers, or any other relevant details.

Once the contact information is extracted, Website Contact Collector allows you to upload it directly to your marketing agent's Google Sheets. This integration enables you to assign tasks efficiently, ensuring that your marketing team has access to the most up-to-date information for their campaigns.

Whether you're a solo telemarketer or part of a marketing team, Website Contact Collector simplifies the process of gathering leads and assigning tasks, helping you boost productivity and drive results in your marketing efforts.
